00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:53,230
I've had enough of such life.

159
00:11:53,230 --> 00:11:54,440
Let's have a life

160
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,670
in a place that

161
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,670
nobody knows us, OK?

162
00:11:58,550 --> 00:11:59,030
OK.

