00:12:21,150 --> 00:12:23,550
into the statue in the hall of the temple.

166
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:25,520
After I calmed down,

167
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:27,230
I decided to

168
00:12:28,230 --> 00:12:31,910
make this temple bustling

169
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:34,110
all the time.

170
