00:13:26,230 --> 00:13:27,350
but to

188
00:13:27,350 --> 00:13:28,400
kill him.

189
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:33,590
Then, then I imputed it to the plasterer.

190
00:13:34,710 --> 00:13:36,550
But these are all old things.

191
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:38,790
Why did you spread

